s of Russia by project number]]\n*[[Admiral Gorshkov-class frigate]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n{{Commons category|Admiral Grigorovich class frigates}}\n\n==External links==\n{{cite news | url= http://www.rian.ru/defense_safety/20101218/310453755.html\n| title= RIA Novosti: a new frigate is laid down in Kaliningrad for the Russian Navy (in Russian)\n| publisher= RIA Novosti\n| date= December 18, 2010\n| accessdate= }}\n* [http://russianships.info/eng/warships/project_11356.htm All Admiral Grigorovich Class Frigates - Complete Ship List]\n\n{{Admiral Grigorovich-class frigate}}\n{{ColdwarSovietShips}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Admiral Grigorovich-class frigate}}\n[[Category:Frigate classes]]\n[[Category:Admiral Grigorovich-class frigates| ]]\n[[Category:2010s ships]]\n[[Category:Stealth ships]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Russian class of frigates}}\n{|{{Infobox ship begin\n}}\n{{Infobox ship image\n| Ship image= \u0410\u0434\u043c\u0438\u0440\u0430\u043b \u0413\u0440\u0438\u0433\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447.jpg\n| Ship caption= Lead ship ''Admiral Grigorivich'' at anchor\n}}\n{{Infobox ship class overview\n|Name=''Admiral Grigorovich'' class<ref name=\"Flot1\">{{cite web|url=http://flot.com/nowadays/strength/surfaceships/admiral-grigorovich/|title=\"\u0410\u0434\u043c\u0438\u0440\u0430\u043b \u0413\u0440\u0438\u0433\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447\"|language=Russian|accessdate=5 February 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160104233015/http://flot.com/nowadays/strength/surfaceships/admiral-grigorovich/|archive-date=4 January 2016|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|Builders= *[[Yantar Shipyard]], [[Kaliningrad]]\n*[[Goa Shipyard]]\n|Operators= *{{navy|Russia}} \n*{{navy|India}}\n|Class before= *{{sclass2-|Krivak|frigate|4}}\n*{{sclass-|Talwar|frigate|4}}\n|Class after=\n|Subclasses=\n|Cost=\n|Built range=\n|In service range=\n|In commission range=\n|Total ships building=3\n|Total ships planned=8\n|Total ships completed=3\n|Total ship